            style="font-size: clamp(16px, 3vw, 20px); color: var(--comet-silver); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 30px; line-height: 1.6;"
          >
            Professional desktop PC repair services in Romford. We fix blue screens, startup
            failures, hardware faults, overheating, and more. Over 20 years of experience with all
            PC brands and custom-built systems.
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="/contact/" class="space-button space-font"><span aria-hidden="true">🛠️</span> Book Repair</a>
            <a
