              BLUE SCREEN ERRORS
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              Blue screen of death (BSOD) crashes caused by driver conflicts, hardware faults, or
              corrupted Windows files. We diagnose and fix the root cause.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;" aria-hidden="true">⚡</span><h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              STARTUP FAILURES
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              PC won't turn on, stuck on loading screen, or beeping on startup? We identify
              whether it's a power supply, motherboard, or software issue.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;" aria-hidden="true">🔧</span><h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;"
            >
              HARDWARE FAULTS
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              Faulty RAM, failing hard drives, dead power supplies, and motherboard issues. We
              test, diagnose, and replace defective components.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;" aria-hidden="true">🌡️</span><h3
