            >
              OVERHEATING
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              PC shutting down from heat? We clean dust build-up, replace thermal paste, fix or
              replace fans, and improve airflow.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

